Now, you were born in .. in
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Britannia Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, Hoxton
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Britannia Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, Hoxton.
 When was this - 1880, 1890?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 1887
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 1887. What was your father's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 May father was a cow-keeper - in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Britannia Street{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}, and he had 15 cows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Where were they kept?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Under the shop!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What sort of shop was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 A milk shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Milk and butter only - not like it is today, tea and goodness knows what. There was just milk and butter, milk and butter and eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Just a dairy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Just a dairy - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And had he any employers - employees?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cf6\insrsid14156104  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh yes. We had a cow-man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Who milked the cows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 The cowman
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes. Anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No. Only my mother in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 She helped. Was it quite a big house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh no, not very large.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 About how many rooms have you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, you've got me guessing now. I should say about five - five rooms I should think, no bathroom or anything like that!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You didn't bath in those days did you!!!!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What sort of a district was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Very poor, and people come in for milk in a - washing jug, you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, I know
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And - no cans. Had a horse and cart but you \'85\'85...
\par <pagez2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Just one milk urn at the back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 It was your father's horse and cart?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And what did he use it for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Just for milk round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 He had a milk round as well as a shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 About how big an area would he go round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh I couldn't tell you dear
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You were saying that you were exercising the cows every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Every Friday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Hmm. And where did they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 The whole length of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Britannia Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 and back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 It wasn't very far, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
Not very far, no. But it was an exercise, you see, and they were all washed down, the backs of them were washed down every day - and their tails washed. (laughter)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 They must have been a bit squashed under the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, they wasn't in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I mean underneath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh no - it was a large cowshed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Hmm, built under the shop, you see, and as the cows came in they went down the slope you see, into the shed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How large a family were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 13
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Gosh! Where abouts were you in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, I was - John, Fred, Arthur, Ben, - I was the fifth
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Had you any help at all or did your mother manage it all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, my mother managed it all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Quite a lot of work?
\par <pagez3>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh yes. Well, they had to work in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cf1\insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cf1\insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How many girls were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Well - there was one girl, and as one girl was born so one died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I see!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 That was strange wasn't it? As
 another girl was born so one died and I had one sister only out of all those children there was only one girl - and she was killed with the last doodle bomb that came over - but on the evening of the bomb, on the evening my brother will went round and sa
w
 her and said 'now,' he said, 'you go down in the cellar tonight and I'll make you up a bed down there'. There were going to the pictures but they thought they wouldn't and he made her a bed up down in the cellar and the whole of the house collapsed but a
 beam or something must've come across just enough to hold the weight off her and she was killed with the blast. Her clock was going on her hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How old were you when you started school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, about 6 or 7 I suppose.
