Half past five till half past twelve at night, and all the staff had was just a couple of hours in the afternoon, you know. Like one barmaid would be resting in the day and then she'd be on all day tomorrow and the next one resting and so on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How much was half a pint?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 ld.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I was going to say, it wasn't much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 It wasn't as much as it is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 ld. for half a pint, 2d. a pint, 4d. a quart.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 It was good beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16409941 Oh, it was lovely beer, lovely}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104  beer. The only 
people that sell it today which I think is anything like it is Watneys, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16409941 W}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 atneys they used to go in for three half pence of gin. Three halfpence}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16409941  of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 gin and two out. Well, the two out was a measure, you see, a measure for three halfpence of gin.
\par <pagez14>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did they drink it neat or did they put anything with it like they do now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, nothing with it, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Would they have the gin and then the beer after it, would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Beg your pardon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, that was in the dairy. They were very particular with the milk you know then, and he carried a cane under his am, and a cane}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16409941 ..}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104  I suppose my eldest brother was a bit inquisitive and he followed up behind and that came towards his eye and he only had one eye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Good gracious!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 He had a glass eye
 you know, but he only had one eye through this cane, and the Excise man couldn't do enough for him. So if there was anything wrong that day it wasn't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16409941 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 ecorded
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10822413 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104  it was too much. My wife was a good help to me with the chickens and ducks and all that. When she was confined it was a different sort of life altogether

\par <pagez15>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you do anything to help with the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Would you ever change nappies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes. I liked taking him out in the pram. Before that I used to take him out in my arms. I was proud to take him out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Was there anyone you and your wife could talk to to ask for advice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Her mother lived in Stoke Newington. She used to see her every week. She used to send her five shillings every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you and your wife discuss bringing up the child? Did you disagree at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No. I wanted a girl for the first but it was a boy. Then we had four girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What arrangement did you have about spending money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I used to give my wife something to spend eve
ry week and then I would pay the bills like gas; later on, about nine years later, I used to give her all the money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What made you do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Because she was better off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did your wife give up work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she ever work again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you help your wife in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, everything that I could do: washing up and things like that.
\par <pagez17>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Have you any idea how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, no. My father died at 41.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And you were, roughly speaking, how old then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 About 8.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, well, I can work that one out. And now about your mother; how old was she compared with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 My mother died - she was 84; and she was a year older than my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You said that your father was a cow keeper at one time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And also had an antique business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And was a prize}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10822413  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 fighter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 A man of many things. Do you ever remember him being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What about your mother, did she have a job before she married your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she ever work after she married him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Never worked. Only, you know, as housekeeper, looking after the children and all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she serve in the shop, where there was the dairy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I don't think so. She did 8 hours pianoforte practice each day, so she wouldn't have much time for assisting in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How did she fit in that pianoforte practi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10822413 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 ing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 She started practi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10822413 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
ing - I'm talking now of when she was 11 years of age That's when she started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 When you were children, did she still manage to play at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, always played, yes.
\par <pagez18>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you have anybody living with you, lodgers, or relations, at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Not that I know of. Had a maid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Living in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Was that all through your childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What duties did she have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, general, I suppose you'd call it. Not cooking. My mother did all the cooking. Just general, you know, looking after the children and putting us to b
ed and all those sort of things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you have the same one, or did you have lots of different ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, same one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What was her name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Do you remember how you got on with her when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did your mother make or mend the clothing of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she make \'85.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she make any of the clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, no. They were bought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Where were they bought from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 in Islington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What sort of shop is that? Is it an outfitters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 It was very much like \'85 haberdashery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Do you remember your father doing anything to help at all in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And what about you and your brothers? And you had one sister, didn't you
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, one sister.
\par <pagez19>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you have any jobs to do in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did I have any jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Nothing at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What about things like cleaning shoes, who did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 All did our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you have to help look after your younger brothers and sister at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 The maid did all that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 When you were a child, do you remember if you had to go to bed at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, always in bed by 7.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You said the maid used to put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Until what age was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 About 12, I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Was your mother usually in, in the evening when you went to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Always in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she come to say 'good night' to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What were the sleeping arrangements of the family? How many bedrooms did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You're talking about when I was about 8, aren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
