\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Were you obliged to eat everything that was served, or could you pick and choose?
