No. I got hit once; now what was it for? Oh, I know my father, he didn't hit me for it, but he toed me for it with the toe of his boot on my bottom and I said 'Oh, me heart, oh, me heart' and my father said, 'It's the first time I knew that your he
art was in your breeches', but what it was over I don't know.
