\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes. More from my mother, you see, because I was with her longer, you see.
