\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 That's your maternal grandmother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 My mother's mother. My father's people lived in Hartford Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
When your mother was ill, or when she was confined you're your younger brothers and sisters, did she have help from any of her relations? Did they come and help her at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How did she manage, then, when she was in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
The doctor would recommend a nurse. She had one of the finest doctors there was, that was Dr. Barratt, and that was the Prince - Edward VII - Prince of Wales's doctor. He got into - he had a big family, 12 in family \'85 12 ... 1
2 children and he became poor and my father, being a bailiff, had to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9642210 distrain}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
 on him, and my father went in, looked round. He said, 'that's a nice picture; that's a nice picture; that's a nice picture. I'm going out now, 'he said, 'and take those to a cert
ain place' and he would get cleared. That means to say that my father would not necessary to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9642210 distrain}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
 on him. So he had enough money to clear it. After that Dr. Barratt and my father were very good friends
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And was it after that he became your doctor, or before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 When you were a schoolchild, did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, only \'85 no, only children's hobbies, you know, iron hoops, and ... Yes. Swimming.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Was that just at the school swimming}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid215508  pool}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
, or did you have swimming nearby your home?
\par <pagez39>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 We had swimming by our home and we had swimming at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And you were keen on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Swimming school. Bathing school
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I don't think so. It might have been a 
penny, or two pence. I don't know, I think it was more farthings in those days, because, if we had any sweets at all \'85 yes, it would be either a penny or a farthing, '}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid215508 cos}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14156104  you'd go into the shop and you'd buy a farthing piece of chocolate. Fry's chocolate, it used to be a penny \'85 four squares for a penny. If you only had a farthing, well, you'd buy a farthings-worth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You said you were always fighting with your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you fight with your sister, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Was there one brother you felt particularly close to, or were you the same with all of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, all of them. We were all \'85 all very good friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You got along well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, well, we'd have a fight over a toy, or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 When you were a child, or a schoolboy, were you conscious of belonging to a particular social class or group in society?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, very quiet. Mostly on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 But I mean as a family, were you aware of belonging to a certain social class as compared with other people, being a bit above them, or \'85?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You weren't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
Were you brought up to treat people of one kind differently from another at all? Sometimes, you know, in the country people I've spoken to about these days said they would be taught to say 'sir' and 'madam' to certain people.
\par <pagez40>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Touch their caps, that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Do you remember people showing respect to your parents in that way? By calling them 'sir', or 'madam'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 In the district where you lived who would you say were generally considered to be the most important people? At that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Trades people. Tailor, wheelwright, photographer yes, mostly the trades people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And what other people did the trades people associate with? In their social life. Or did they mostly just associate with each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Do you think that your mother and father had the same attitude to people in different social classes - you know, poorer working people ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 They shared the same attitudes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Do you remember anyone being described at that time as 'a real gentleman' or 'a real lady'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You would say she was a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Real lady.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What sort of qualities do you think are those that a real lady has?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Speech, behaviour and dress.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What particularities of dress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Mostly what I can realise that \'85
 a nice black velvet dress, and hair, black hair done in a plait round and round and round and round and round. Hair dressed up nicely and who dresses nicely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you think that the police treated some people differently from others when you were a boy?
\par <pagez41>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you ever come into contact with the police?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Could you tell me about an occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes. Well, where we lived they used to have a post at the corner of the street, and they were very much like a gun with a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid215508 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 ound top, you know. We used to jump over them. Well, if we get up to mischief - we used to get up to mischief, you kno
w - and the policeman came after us, he used to have a black glove and balls, you know, little glass balls in his fingers, and if you did anything wrong and he came up to you, he'd hit you with those. Well, we used to have a lark with the policeman. When 
you did something wrong, perhaps in the street that the children would be playing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid402157  \{blank\}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 , something like that \'85 that's a pan that you use for \'85
 kick about like a football. If the policeman came along he didn't like that. We were playing in the road, and yo
u shouldn't play in the road, he'd come after us. Then we'd go along 'till we came to a place where the posts were a bit too close for him to get through and we'd dodge through there, look out from the other side and laugh at him. (laughter) Then there wa
s another thing we used to do. That was a policeman on beat, he would get dry, so he would find a doorway to go in then we would know that the barman was apt to take him over a pint of beer or half a pint of beer. There at night when we'd \'85
 closing up at half past 12, we had a dog called Dick, he was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid402157 \{blank\} }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 terrier, and that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid402157 \{blank\} }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 terrier used to get out before we closed the public house and stop out and he'd parade all night with the policeman. Different policeman, different policemen changed over, you k
now, different police, and that, the old dog would still be with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Your first job, I think I'm right in saying, was at a jewellers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Silversmiths and jewellers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How old were you when you took that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I'm not sure, 14 or 15.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Had you earned any money in any other way before you took that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And you said that you were quite good at making chains?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 But you didn't like going out for tea? You didn't like going out to get tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, no.
\par <pagez42>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Why did you object to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 It wasn't a nice job. You took a long pole and you had about 8 or 9 beer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9642210  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14156104 cans on it, you'd go into a coffee shop with others, and we were a bit of a high standard I suppose, and didn't like mixing with the other two boys. And I didn't like that job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 The other two boys used to come with you with the pole, did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes. Not from the same firm, they were from different firms, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Oh, you didn't like mixing with the other boys in the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Why do you think that was, do you think perhaps because you'd been to a different sort of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Might have been, yes. Might have been. It wasn't a nice job, if one was standing in a coffee shop waiting for \'85
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You mean you had to spend quite a lot of time in that coffee shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, waiting them to be filled up and all that lark. It's not a nice job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 When you became a road engineer how did you get on with the other people there that you came into contact with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Very well. I was a pal, I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Well, you had a very good wage for a young man at that time, didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 When you started this road engineer work, did you still live at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you ever belong to a trade union at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Not at that time. I did belong to a trade union, but 30 years later.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 But at that time you didn't belong to any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you feel that employers and workers had different interests at that time, even though you didn't belong to a trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You mean you didn't have views on that?
\par <pagez43>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you feel there was a division between, say, craftsmen, skilled workers and unskilled workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No. Yes, your craftsman fancied himself a bit, if I might p
ut it that way and your other man, the assistant craftsman was an underdog. But later on as years went on it differed. But at the start your assistant was a mate and you would treat him as a mate. Sometimes it was like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 You mean, later on, as years passed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 As years passed it altered, but at that time\'85
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 People kept to different things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes, they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Would you say that going out to work changed your ideas about life, your attitude to life, and yourself in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I got on well with everybody, so I mean to say, it's not necessary to change.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I just wondered if that contact with other people with other kinds of life made you change?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I think you said you were about 25 when you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 So that was about 1912?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes. Yes, it would be 1912.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Could you tell me where you met your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes. My brother had a sweetheart, my wife was the sweetheart's friend. That's how we met.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you know her long before you decided to get married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Well, yes. I met her when she was 17 and I would've been about 19 then. From 19 to 25, six years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she have living parents at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par <pagez44>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How did you get along with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Very well indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 When you wanted to marry her, did you do what some people did at that time - and some people still do - did you go and speak to her father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you save up before getting married
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you get any help in setting up your first home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, it wasn't necessary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did your wife work before she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What sort of work did she do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 She was a dressmaker and she used to do a lot of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9642210 fur}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
 work and she used to use her own hair for cotton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 How very original. Was that usual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 What colour was her hair then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Light, brown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did you have a large wedding, or a small one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Rather a large wedding, yes. Three horses - no motors then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 And about how many guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I should think 30 or 40.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Were you able to go away for a honeymoon? After the wedding? Or did you go back to work straight away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No, no I went straight back to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Did she go on working as a dressmaker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 She stopped work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Yes.
\par <pagez45>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Where did you live after the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9642210  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid402157 \{blank\}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9642210  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
Road, Walthamstow, a little flat. And my hobby then was chickens \'85 I had 40 white }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid402157 \{blank\} }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 
chickens, I had a Great Dane, I had two sporting Retriever dogs and I had an Airedale dog and no children. (laughter)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I'd have thought you hardly had room for children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 I had a lovely garden, and as soon as the first child came along I got rid of all of them, bar one dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1470074 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Why was that? No time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8879510 GK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14156104 Well, it was too much. See, my wife was a big help to me with the chickens and dogs, and all that. When she was confined
